    "In total, they contain 700 manuallyannotated pages, 753 manually-annotated chemical images, and 364 precisely annotated molecular graphs (MOL files 26).",
    "More details can be found in the \"Methods\" section below.",
    "Table 3 presents the performances of these three key ingestion steps.",
    "It shows the precision and recall of the page segmentation, the image classification, and the chemical-structure recognition, and for DECIMER-Segmentation and MolGrapher, a comparison with state-ofthe-art models.",
    "For the recognition module, the precision is computed using InChIKey 27 equality, ignoring stereo-chemistry."
